Dialogue: 1,0:25:19.82,0:25:23.99,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}They will finally feel the flames
Dialogue: 1,0:25:24.17,0:25:28.36,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Flames that run down through my veins
Dialogue: 1,0:25:28.70,0:25:32.71,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}I will make this city burn
Dialogue: 1,0:25:32.92,0:25:37.07,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}We’re not planning to return
Dialogue: 1,0:25:37.92,0:25:41.75,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Trying so hard to be free
Dialogue: 1,0:25:42.09,0:25:45.35,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}To make you see what I see
Dialogue: 1,0:25:46.75,0:25:50.59,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Hold on to your wishes
