Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.17,0:25:28.36,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}在我血管中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.70,0:25:32.71,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}火光照亮城市
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.92,0:25:37.07,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一去不复返
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:41.75,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}为了自由而奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.09,0:25:45.35,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}为了你我能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.75,0:25:50.59,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}坚持你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.59,0:25:54.24,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果不再对我期待
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.58,0:25:57.36,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}原谅我让你失望
